- Framework: Next.js 15 (App Router, React Server Components)
- AI SDK v5 for LLM integration with streaming
- Drizzle ORM + PostgreSQL
- NextAuth.js v5
- Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- Optional: Redis for resumable streaming (via `resumable-stream`); configured with `REDIS_URL`.
- Optional: Berget AI models via OpenAI-compatible provider when `BERGET_AI_API_KEY` is set.
- Key directories:
  - `app/` (auth, chat)
  - `lib/` (ai, db, artifacts, editor)
  - `components/`
  - `artifacts/`
  - `hooks/`
  - `tests/`
